<DOCNO> FBIS3-4909 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas041_d_94016" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-041 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  2 Mar 1994 </DATE1>

