<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tokyo, February 28 (KNS-KCNA) [dateline as received] 
-- A meeting of Korean educationists and scientists in Japan 
took place in Osaka on February 26 to express thanks to the 
great leader Generalissimo Kim Il-song and the dear leader 
Marshal Kim Chong-il for the 126th instalment of educational aid 
fund and stipends. 
  It was attended by O Hyong-chin, vice-chairman of the 
