Korean Teachers in Japan, said the entire educational workers, 
bearing deep in mind the solicitude repeatedly shown by the 
great leader and the dear leader, should more successfully 
promote national education with the meaningful 50th anniversary 
of the August 15 national liberation, 40th anniversary of the 
formation of Chongnyon and 17th congress of Chongnyon one year 
ahead. 
  A letter to Generalissimo Kim Il-song was adopted at the 
meeting. 

