Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, March 2 (KCNA) -- The birthday of the 
dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il was celebrated in different 
countries. 
  A celebration meeting was held at the building of the 
Nicaraguan Association of Democratic Lawyers. 
  Chairman of the Nicaragua-Korea Friendship and Solidarity 
Association Albaro Ramirez Gonsalez in his speech stressed that 
the Nicaraguan people were significantly celebrating the 
birthday of Comrade Kim Chong-il together with the Korean people. 
  He said: "Dear Comrade Kim Chong-il is an illustrious 
leader who is constantly exalting socialism with his outstanding 
idea and theory and his energetic leadership. The Korean people 
are holding him in high esteem and creditably building 
Korean-style socialism under his wise leadership." 
  Meanwhile, a seminar on the chuche idea was held at the 
independence study centre of Bangladesh and a seminar on 
Nepal-Korea friendly relations at the National Press Club of 
Nepal. 
  DPRK book, photo and handiwork exhibitions, film shows, 
photo 
illustrations, lectures and other functions were arranged in 
Islamabad, Pakistan, the House of the Nepal Academy of Sciences, 
a City House of Culture of Poland, Khodenka Exhibition-Gallery 
in northwest administrative district of Moscow, the Banat Museum 
in Timisoara of Romania, a company of Thailand, Abidja state of 
Nigeria, Helsinki, the National Youth Union of Algeria, the 
Cultural Palace of Workers in Yanji, Jilin Province, China, and 
the group for the study of the chuche idea of the Pugura Club of 
the Malta Labour Party. 
  A performance of "Art Evening of February" was given in 
Tokyo 
and a "national table tennis competition for February 16 cup" 
was sponsored by the Mongolia-Korea Friendship Association and 
the Mongolian Table Tennis Federation at the gymnasium of the 
sports college of Mongolia. 

</TEXT>

