Minister Lt. Gen. Myint Aung, Hotels and Tourism Minister Lt. 
Gen. Kyaw Ba, Indian and Japanese ambassadors, American and 
Singaporean charge d'affaires, departmental heads and advisers 
from the ministry of forestry affairs, responsible personnel, 
and relatives. 
