<F P=106> [Seoul--KYODO/YONHAP] </F>
  [Text] Deng Xiaoping, the supreme leader of China, handed 
out a directive to policy makers in China to fully support the 
North Korean economic reform policy and to help realize North 
Korean President Kim Il-song's visit to China. This was 
